      <title>德国保守党暂停对移民法案进行有争议的投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/german-conservatives-pause-controversial-vote-on-migration-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国保守党派周五请求议会下院休会，这一迹象表明，在极右翼的支持下，德国保守党派计划通过一项强硬的移民法案，导致局势紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/german-conservatives-pause-controversial-vote-on-migration-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 10:15:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>总统顾问称尼日利亚需要大幅提高电价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/nigeria-needs-much-higher-power-prices-president-s-adviser-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布的能源特别顾问表示，尼日利亚的电价需要上涨约三分之二，才能反映出供电成本，预计几个月内电价就会上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/nigeria-needs-much-higher-power-prices-president-s-adviser-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 10:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>更多中国间谍嫌疑人浮出水面 马科斯“非常不安”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/marcos-very-disturbed-as-more-suspected-chinese-spies-surface</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统费迪南德·马科斯对菲律宾逮捕的中国间谍嫌疑犯人数不断增加深表担忧，这促使安全官员加强了监控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/marcos-very-disturbed-as-more-suspected-chinese-spies-surface</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 10:03:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
