    <item>
      <title>奥尔班再次威胁否决俄罗斯对天然气运输的制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/orban-renews-threat-to-veto-russia-sanctions-over-gas-transit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班再次威胁说，如果乌克兰未能在六个月内恢复俄罗斯天然气输送，他将在欧盟对俄罗斯的制裁到期时否决制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/orban-renews-threat-to-veto-russia-sanctions-over-gas-transit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 07:36:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸军方再次延长紧急状态，推迟选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/myanmar-generals-extend-emergency-rule-again-delaying-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[缅甸军政府延长为期四年的紧急状态，由于内战持续不断，长期承诺的大选计划进一步推迟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/myanmar-generals-extend-emergency-rule-again-delaying-polls</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 07:12:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与主要贸易伙伴展开关税对决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-barrels-toward-tariff-showdown-with-canada-mexico-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普准备于周六征收第一波关税，这将促使外国政府和企业纷纷避开潜在的关税并准备采取报复措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-barrels-toward-tariff-showdown-with-canada-mexico-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 00:03:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普第二次攻击全球气候秩序</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-01-30/the-global-climate-order-teeters-under-second-assault-by-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普第二次退出《巴黎协定》，对气候行动来说，这是一个更加动荡的时期，民粹主义的兴起和企业的撤退给美国撤退增加了更大的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-01-30/the-global-climate-order-teeters-under-second-assault-by-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 14:39:07 GMT</pubDate>
